                    <comment id="12379290" author="oglueck" created="Wed, 17 Jul 2002 23:49:23 +0100"  >The above patch contains the following changes:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
- Proxy Authentication&lt;br/&gt;
- SSL tunneling through proxies (ConnectMethod)&lt;br/&gt;
- free choice of the SSLSocketFactory&lt;br/&gt;
- setting SO_TIMEOUT from HttpClient&lt;br/&gt;
- POST method accepts InputStream as body&lt;br/&gt;
- POST and PUT do not follow redirects by default&lt;br/&gt;
- GetMethod: doc&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
